Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:27.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方叫做稻村崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:28.11,S3,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1200A0&\pos(1518,875)\fad(530,0)}稻村崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是江之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,江之岛 看得到江之岛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,天气好的话 富士山就会清晰地出现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:42.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在行合桥的红绿灯这里转弯之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:50.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会到我们要去的店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,冲冲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:53.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:57.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好高端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:22:59.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:00.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:05.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是万众期望的阿玛尔菲咖啡馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里仿佛置身于意大利的阿玛尔菲一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:22.25,S5,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\blur10\fad(521,0)\3c&HB356EB&\pos(1416,801)\b1}Delezie al limone
